e who are constant in prayer and spend on others out of what We provide for them as sustenance:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1163.mp3","surahId":8,"words":[{"id":2196,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/008_003_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2197,"position":2,"arabic":"يُقِيمُونَ","translation":"প্রতিষ্ঠা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_003_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2198,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ","translation":"সালাত","audioUrl":"wbw/008_003_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2199,"position":4,"arabic":"وَمِمَّا","translation":"ও (তা) হতে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/008_003_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2200,"position":5,"arabic":"رَزَقْنَـٰهُمْ","translation":"আমরা জীবিকা দিয়েছি তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/008_003_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2201,"position":6,"arabic":"يُنفِقُونَ","translation":"তারা ব্যয় করে","audioUrl":"wbw/008_003_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2202,"position":7,"arabic":"٣","translation":"(৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":4,"arabic":"أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ حَقًّۭا ۚ لَّهُمْ دَرَجَٰتٌ عِندَ رَبِّهِمْ وَمَغْفِرَةٌۭ وَرِزْقٌۭ كَرِيمٌۭ","translation":"it is they, they who are truly believers! Theirs shall be great dignity in their Sustainer's sight, and forgiveness of sins, and a most excellent sustenance.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1164.mp3","surahId":8,"words":[{"id":3518,"position":1,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"ঐসব(লোক)","audioUrl":"wbw/008_004_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3519,"position":2,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারাই","audioUrl":"wbw/008_004_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3520,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"মু'মিন","audioUrl":"wbw/008_004_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3521,"position":4,"arabic":"حَقًّۭا ۚ","translation":"প্রকৃত","audioUrl":"wbw/008_004_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3523,"positio